<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>OneLink Access Request</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .user-details {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .cta-button {
      background-color: #fd5901;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <img src="https://thecapitalhub.in/static/media/logo-white.c4e4dacf1f6283c93e11.png" alt="CapitalHub Logo" style="max-width: 400px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h2>New OneLink Access Request</h2>
    
    <p>You have received a new OneLink access request for your startup.</p>
    
    <div class="user-details">
      <h3>User Details:</h3>
      <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= userName %></p>
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= userEmail %></p>
      <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= userPhone %></p>
    </div>

    <p>You can manage this request from your dashboard:</p>
    
    <a href="https://thecapitalhub.in/company-profile" class="cta-button">View Request</a>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>The CapitalHub Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 